<h1 id='orders'>Orders</h1><h2 id='create-authenticated-tracking-uri'>Create Authenticated Tracking Uri</h2><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://api.connectxpo.com/orders/&lt;ID&gt;/authenticted-tracking-uri?bu=&lt;BU&gt;"</span>
  -X POST
  -H <span class="s2">"Authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN"</span>
</code></pre>
<blockquote>
<p>JSON Response:</p>
</blockquote>
<pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="s2">"orderId"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">'ORDER_ID'</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="s2">"uri"</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"https://track.xpo.com/?orderid=..."</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>
<p>This endpoint can be used to generate an authentucated URI for the XPO Logistics tracking page</p>
<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>POST https://api.connectxpo.com/orders/&lt;ID&gt;/authenticted-tracking-uri?bu=&lt;BU&gt;</code></p>
<h3 id='url-parameters'>URL Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
<th>Valid Values</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>ID</td>
<td>The id of the order</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>BU</td>
<td>The business unit the order belongs to</td>
<td><a href="#business-units">Business Units</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
